title: Play Like the Pros at World Woods Golf Club
text:
Updated: 2:09 p.m. Thursday, Aug. 13, 2015 | Posted: 5:26 a.m. Thursday, Aug. 13, 2015 Play Like the Pros at World Woods Golf Club 
Take a quick look at the World Woods Golf Club in Brooksville. The club features Tom Fazio's Pine Barrens and Rolling Oaks golf courses and the No. 1 ranked golf practice facility and driving range.
